<HEADLINE> Two Soldiers Of U.N.Peace Keeping Force In Angola Killed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, April 3 (Xinhua) -- Two soldiers of the United Nations
peace keeping force in Angola were killed and the other was
seriously injured today when their car was attacked by
unidentified armed men, the Angola News Agency reported.
</P>
