peace in the Middle East based on restoring the legitimate rights
of the Arab people and terminating Israeli occupation of Arab
territories in Palestine, the Golan Heights and south Lebanon.
</P>
<P>
This is the road to genuine, just and lasting peace which may
guarantee regional security, stability and peaceful coexistence,
the official said. 
