<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 3 (Xinhua) -- The China National Ostrich Farming
and Development Association (CNOFDA) hosted an ostrich eggshell
painting show, the first of its kind in China, at the China Art
Galley April 2-7.
</P>
<P>
The exquisite paintings are done on more than 100 ostrich
eggshells by outstanding contemporary artists, including Gu Yuan,
Yin Shoushi and Han Meilin.
</P>
