Meanwhile, a group of ostrich-related art products such as
bags, shoes and hats are on display, as well as some pictures of
ostriches.
</P>
<P>
Wang said that the association plans to display the arts and
crafts in Guangzhou, Shanghai, Hong Kong, Macao and Taiwan, as
well as Japan, to boost the ostrich farming business and develop
the market for ostrich eggshell paintings.  
