mail, but hand it over instead to the police for immediate
forensic scrutiny.
</P>
<P>
Some of opposition parties and mass organizations have
differed from the government's stand on the way of adopting draft
constitution. They have insisted that a new constitution be
adopted by a constituent assembly and a national referendum.
