<HEADLINE> Mugabe Urges For High Standard Morals For Children </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, April 3 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwean President Robert Mugabe
on Tuesday called on parents to help their children foster a high
standard of morals against promiscuity.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a fund raising function for the country's AIDS
victims, Mugabe attributed the rising incidence of HIV infection
to sexual immorality.
</P>
<P>
