<HEADLINE> European Olympic Boxing Qualifying Results (2-last) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
75 kg:
</P>
<P>
Ludovik Plachetka, Czech, bt Eric van den Heuvel, Netherlands,
pts (13-10)
